About Tarpon Bay Grill & Tiki Bar
Looking for some good old Florida Fun? Want to unwind and listen to some music and enjoy great food? The Tarpon Bay Grill & Tiki Bar is the place to be.
We have a great live music schedule and some of the best food in town! Located in the Ramada Inn on Route 41 in Sarasota we are a great venue for families!
Every Monday and Wednesday from 4-7pm is Bingo, Taco Buffet on Tuesdays from 6-9pm, AUCE Shimp & Fish on Fridays. Bring your friends and family.
You will love our outdoor Tiki Bar. We have a fabulous selection of beer, wine and liquor!
So, check us out. You will love the atmosphere and you can chill out starting at 11am every day.

Builder #page
Let Us Host Your Next Event
Tarpon Bay Grill is truly a unique destination to host memorable events. Inside and outside venue, pool, volleyball, and waterfront gazebo, allow us to use creativity in planning every event. We will work with you to select the area best suited for you and your guests. Our attention to detail and friendly team will make it a joyful day to be remembered. Our venue is right-sized to host small and large events. In addition, if accommodations are required, we will coordinate your stay on the property with our partners at the Ramada Inn.
Hosting one of the following:
Wedding
Birthday Party
Family Reunion
Sporting Team Function
Bachelor/Bachelorette Party
Couples Shower
Baby Shower
Bridal Shower
Class Reunion
Or any other reason for celebrating…..
